<p>Hello <%= @recipient.first_name.presence || @recipient.email %>,</p>

<p>Your 30-day Miru Pro trial for <%= @company.name %> is now active.</p>

<p>
  Trial ends on <%= @trial_ends_at&.in_time_zone(@company.timezone.presence || Time.zone)&.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %>.
</p>

<p>
  You can review billing and upgrade any time from
  <a href="<%= @billing_url %>"><%= @billing_url %></a>.
</p>
